---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import Container from '../components/Container.astro';
import SectionHeading from '../components/SectionHeading.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="About | Tajinder Singh" description="About Tajinder Singh, Solutions Architect focused on automation and edge/data systems.">
	<Container size="wide">
		<section class="section">
			<SectionHeading
				eyebrow="About"
				title="Architecture That Reduces Operational Drag"
				description="I work at the intersection of edge infrastructure, automation, and data systems."
			/>
			<div class="about-copy">
				<p>
					I'm Tajinder Singh (Taj), a solutions architect focused on designing systems that are reliable in
					production - not just clean in diagrams. My work centers on automation-heavy platforms that require strong
					edge verification, structured event flows, and practical observability.
				</p>
				<p>
					Across platform and client work, I design routing layers, verification pipelines, and event-driven
					architectures that teams can operate without constant firefighting.
				</p>
				<p>
					My approach is simple: clarify constraints early, design for failure modes upfront, and prioritize
					architectures that create operational leverage rather than complexity.
				</p>
				<p>
					I am particularly interested in systems that combine edge enforcement, automation, and search - areas
					where small architectural decisions have large operational impact. Outside of active projects, I explore
					ways to make verification paths safer, workflows more observable, and platform design more predictable.
				</p>
				<h3 class="about-subheading">Research & Continuous Development</h3>
				<p>
					Alongside platform architecture work, I am completing a Level 7 AI and Data Science apprenticeship. My
					focus includes statistical modeling, model validation, feature engineering, and production considerations
					for machine learning systems.
				</p>
				<p>
					This training strengthens the analytical foundation behind my work in search architecture, automation
					systems, and data-driven platform design.
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="section split">
			<article class="card">
				<h2>What I Focus On</h2>
				<ul>
					<li><strong>Edge Verification & Request Governance</strong> Hardened entry layers that validate, sanitize, and control traffic before it reaches core systems.</li>
					<li><strong>Automation & Event Architecture</strong> Resilient, observable pipelines that replace brittle manual operations.</li>
					<li><strong>Search & Data Platforms</strong> Structured ingestion, schema governance, and faceted discovery systems that scale beyond browser or CMS constraints.</li>
					<li><strong>API & Service Orchestration</strong> Clear contracts, safe routing, and failure-aware integration patterns across distributed services.</li>
				</ul>
			</article>
			<article class="card">
				<h2>Highlights</h2>
				<ol class="timeline">
					<li>
						<strong>2026 - Verification-First Intake Architecture</strong>
						<p>Shipped a hardened submission gateway linking public forms to downstream workflows with strict authenticity and token validation.</p>
					</li>
					<li>
						<strong>2025 - Faceted Search Platform</strong>
						<p>Designed and deployed a scalable server-side search layer supporting 50k+ indexed products.</p>
					</li>
					<li>
						<strong>2025 - Smart Edge Caching & Asset Protection</strong>
						<p>Reduced origin load and improved cache predictability through structured edge controls.</p>
					</li>
					<li>
						<strong>Ongoing - Event Architecture Advisory</strong>
						<p>Supporting teams transitioning to structured, event-driven automation models.</p>
					</li>
				</ol>
			</article>
		</section>
	</Container>
</MainLayout>

<style>
	.section {
		margin-bottom: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 5rem);
	}

	.about-copy {
		max-width: 56rem;
		display: grid;
		gap: 0.8rem;
	}

	.about-subheading {
		margin: 0.35rem 0 0;
		font-size: 1.08rem;
		line-height: 1.3;
		color: var(--color-text);
	}

	.split {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
		gap: 1rem;
	}

	.card {
		padding: 1.2rem;
		border-radius: var(--radius-md);
		border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
		background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-bg-elevated) 90%, transparent);
	}

	.card h2 {
		font-size: 1.3rem;
		margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
	}

	.card ul {
		margin: 0;
		padding-left: 1.15rem;
		display: grid;
		gap: 0.65rem;
	}

	.timeline {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
		margin: 0;
		display: grid;
		gap: 0.95rem;
	}

	.timeline li {
		padding-left: 0.85rem;
		border-left: 2px solid var(--color-border);
	}

	.timeline p {
		margin: 0.25rem 0 0;
	}

	@media (max-width: 900px) {
		.split {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
	}
</style>
